  | id = 
  | accessdate = 2012-02-23}}, p.1692,  on  [http://nova.stanford.edu/~vlf/  VLF Group website, Stanford Univ.]</ref> also referred to as an '''earth dipole antenna''', '''transmission line antenna''',<ref name="Barr" /> and in technical literature as a  '''horizontal electric dipole''' (HED),<ref name="Barr" /><ref name="NavyFactSheet" >{{cite web
